name: Angela White
description:
Australian-born actress and director, well known for her energetic and involved perfomance and winning multiple awards for it too, Angela White!

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. This embedding does not work well for RealisticVisionV1.3! The success rate for the output with this model is abysmal, about 1 in 10. I've reran training the embedding twice and tested many different versions of the embedding made during training, but I can't get the embedding to perform on this model, my apologies. There's a LORA of Angela White on CivitAI, perhaps that will work better with Realistic Vision V1.3!

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Buy Me A Coffee :)
